column2: b'Pokemon Fushigi no Dungeon: Shutsudou Pokemon Kyuujotai Ganbaruzu!'

b"A human wakes up one day to discover that he has become a Squirtle in a world filled with natural disasters, where he meets Charmander and Chikorita of Team Go-Getters, a Pokemon rescue team. Squirtle joins Team Go-Getters for the task of saving Pichu's Brother Pikachu from Skarmory, however Gengar and his Team Meanies decide to interfere.\n\n(Source: ANN)"
